content: vivoidos: Merged 3 PRs this month, including a significant feature PR #536 adding agent selection, router and sidebar layout in React (+2162/-192 lines). Other contributions included adding client configuration to optionally ignore bots and DMs in PR #336 (+54/-18 lines) and refactoring template types in PR #479 (+15/-1 lines). Activity was sporadic, with contributions on only 4 days this month, primarily focused on feature work (50%) and bugfixes (25%).
